    <item>
      <title>贝恩称资产管理公司现在必须投资私募市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/asset-managers-must-invest-in-private-markets-now-bain-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩公司表示，各类资产管理公司如果想避免遭受损失，就需要考虑投资私募市场，同时调整整个策略以应对危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/asset-managers-must-invest-in-private-markets-now-bain-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
