      <title>福特斥资 19 亿美元进军 SUV 业务，进一步退出电动汽车领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ford-pulls-back-further-from-evs-with-1-9-billion-suv-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福特汽车公司再次调整其电气化战略，取消了全电动运动型多功能车的计划，此举可能使该汽车制造商损失约 19 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ford-pulls-back-further-from-evs-with-1-9-billion-suv-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
